OL,3,CNext government must be 'loud and
OL,4,Cproud' about green growth, says CBI
OL,5,Cchief
OL,7,FThe next government cannot be pro-
OL,8,Fgrowth without being pro-green,
OL,9,Faccording to a business leader.
OL,11,FRain Newton-Smith, chief executive of
OL,12,Fthe CBI, will tell a conference in
OL,13,FLondon on Monday that there is a risk
OL,14,Fin trying to "separate the economy
OL,15,Ffrom net zero".
