OL,7,FAs the General Election campaign
OL,8,Fenters its final days, she will
OL,9,Fhighlight the "deafening silence from
OL,10,Fall the parties about the issues of
OL,11,Fclimate change, biodiversity loss, net
OL,12,Fzero and our planet."
OL,14,FResearch by the CBI suggests the next
OL,15,Fgovernment could add as much as #57
OL,16,Fbillion to the economy from green
OL,17,Fgrowth by 2030.
