OL,3,CNext government must be 'loud and
OL,4,Cproud' about green growth, says CBI
OL,5,Cchief
OL,7,F"No more prevarication, no more rowed
OL,8,Fback commitments. Whoever forms the
OL,9,Fnext government has to let the world
OL,10,Fknow it's serious about the investment
OL,11,Fopportunities from net zero and that
OL,12,Fwe're in this for the long haul. Make
OL,13,Fdecisions and stick to them."
OL,15,FShe will add that businesses want the
OL,16,Fcreation of an Office for Net Zero to
OL,17,Fco-ordinate action across government
OL,18,Fdepartments.
