OL,3,CNext government must be 'loud and
OL,4,Cproud' about green growth, says CBI
OL,5,Cchief
OL,7,F"It's a dangerous error to try and
OL,8,Fseparate it (the economy) from net
OL,9,Fzero.
OL,11,F"There is still too much in our
OL,12,Fpolitical discourse that amounts to
OL,13,F'Can we afford to go for net zero?'
OL,14,FBut the real question is, can we
OL,15,Fafford not to?"
